        p.lead Orikami is not your run-of-the-mill data science company. Our company is specialised in helping you innovate <br> with data and learn from data. We are not statisticians. We are computational neuroscientists. We are artificial <br> intelligence scientists. We are real data scientists. We know how to discover relevant patterns in data.
  
